{"tid":592021,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[透澈分析]曼聯敗陣主因","createTime":"2018-03-14T02:15:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T03:04:33.000Z","uid":38683,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fc5318c32f80a679ff378a4398f47f9121852672","tid":592021,"uid":38683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T02:15:24.000Z","msg":"我最主要就係想指一曼聯輸波的最大原因，當然球員和教練都有一定的責任，但我認為最大的問題是反曼的那幫人，我上社交網站上看到，他們日日都在評擊曼聯，是曼聯輸波的關鍵！如果不喜歡曼聯的話，就請支持其他球隊，為什麼日日都想希望曼聯輸波？曼聯這兩季的成績大幅下滑，都是因為那班反曼的7頭日日在咀咒曼聯輸波，而最不幸的是，竟然連個天都幫埋佢地，搞到曼聯打到咁差。 唉！我明白有批評才有進步，但現在的曼聯，真的很需要各隊球迷的支持，才能重震雄風！請停止對曼聯的批評或咀咒，並關閉其有關的專頁和網站！曼聯成績下滑最要主原因是反曼人士不斷的干擾，如果他們的不停止反曼行動的話，那就消滅他們吧！只有這樣做才可以令曼聯做番一隊英超BIG 4！<br />\n死獌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794e5ac2cc5c9ccb70ce800c5ef388283a5fdd94","tid":592021,"uid":38683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T02:16:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65176715c6345f93239ee058acae2872fc0ea761","tid":592021,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T02:56:04.000Z","msg":"善心打破零回覆"},{"pid":"8fcb9d283b6c92f6a8ffd8216eaaaff5c3aeac25","tid":592021,"uid":162809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T03:00:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>善心打破零回覆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />柒鳩"},{"pid":"39e4a8